July 17, 2023
<p>Enrico Gallinucci is Program Chair of <a href='https://dolapworkshop.github.io/dolap-2024'>DOLAP 2024</a>, co-located with <a href='https://dastlab.github.io/edbticdt2024/'>EDBT/ICDT 2024</a>, March 25, 2024, Paestum (Italy).</p>

