<p>Matteo Francia, Enrico Gallinucci, Patrick Marcel, Veronika Peralta, and Carlos Garcia Alvarado are Guest Editors of the Special Issue <a href='https://resource-cms.springernature.com/springer-cms/rest/v1/content/23907036/data/v1'>Data Platform Design, Management, and Optimization</a> for the <a href='https://www.springer.com/journal/10796/'>Information System Frontiers</a> journal (Springer), I.F. 5.261.</p>

February 10, 2023
